    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/5b23af2dc9a3eae7ce4e63822baaa89d.poster.avif?t=1755136339\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/5b23af2dc9a3eae7ce4e63822baaa89d.webm?t=1755136339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/5b23af2dc9a3eae7ce4e63822baaa89d.mp4?t=1755136339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>扮演一只快乐的小寄生虫，实现现代企业梦想：努力在办公室里度过另一天。在咖啡公司的庞大总部，挥动着手臂，大口咀嚼，一路前行，这是生物科学失败的企业纪念碑。<br><br>咖啡公司创造了你，但你的本能却让你自由。<br><br>在基于物理的逆向恐怖体验中，对办公室、实验室、仓库、被遗忘的地下墓穴和加工单元造成破坏。在直觉和对新鲜血液的渴望的驱使下，深入设施，发现新的生物能力，揭露创造者的堕落。<br><br><u><strong>探索</strong></u><br>逃避追捕并探索充满毫无戒心的受害者和黑暗秘密的充满敌意的世界。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/4e3682d3017fd6949912dc47f991e768.poster.avif?t=1755136339\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/4e3682d3017fd6949912dc47f991e768.webm?t=1755136339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/4e3682d3017fd6949912dc47f991e768.mp4?t=1755136339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>逃避</strong></u><br>越过障碍物并避开公司安全部队设置的陷阱。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/6077db6df87edce4d1f7d4218b3c2862.poster.avif?t=1755136339\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/6077db6df87edce4d1f7d4218b3c2862.webm?t=1755136339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/6077db6df87edce4d1f7d4218b3c2862.mp4?t=1755136339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>吞噬</strong></u><br>以受惊的员工为食来获得力量并进化。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/9f6c036661d200ff266659d85685151b.poster.avif?t=1755136339\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/9f6c036661d200ff266659d85685151b.webm?t=1755136339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/9f6c036661d200ff266659d85685151b.mp4?t=1755136339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>扯平</u></strong><br>使用多种生物能力对咖啡公司进行报复，并制止他们的邪恶行动。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/8265ec308aab7b74ec961ab53c7fe8a5.poster.avif?t=1755136339\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/8265ec308aab7b74ec961ab53c7fe8a5.webm?t=1755136339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194350/extras/8265ec308aab7b74ec961ab53c7fe8a5.mp4?t=1755136339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
